  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nSimplify: 15 \\times (5 + 3) \\div 4 - 6\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nFirst, solve the parentheses:\n5 + 3 = 8\nNow the equation becomes:15 \\times 8 \\div 4 - 6\nPerform the multiplication and division: \n\n15 \u00d7 2 \u2212 6\n 30 \u2212 6\n 24\n\nSo, the simplified result is: 24",
